\section*{LVH Criteria}
- Sokolow-Lyon criterium
- R in V 5 or $\mathrm{V} 6+\mathrm{S}$ in $\mathrm{V} 1>35$ mm.
- Cornell-criterium
- R in aVL and S in $\mathrm{V} 3>28$ mm in men
- R in aVL and S in V3 >20 mm in women
