\section*{RVH Criteria}
- R/S ratio in V1 or V3R > 1, or R/S ratio in V5 or V6 <= 1
- R wave in V1 >= 7 mm
- R wave in $\mathrm{V} 1+\mathrm{S}$ wave in V5 or V6 > 10.5 mm
- rSR= in V1 with R'= > 10 mm
- qR complex in V1
- Secondary ST-T changes in right precordial leads
