\section*{LAE}
- Either P wave with a broad ( $>0.04 \mathrm{sec}$ or 1 small square) and deeply negative ( $>1 \mathrm{~mm}$ ) terminal part in V1 P wave duration $>0.12 \mathrm{sec}$ in leads I and / or II
